title: Fredericks & Mae Nautical Flags Domino Set
description:
The Nautical Flag Domino set replaces the standard dot patterns with silkscreened nautical flags, used to communicate numbers 0-6. A visual delight, the Nautical Flag set is sure to please both sailors and landlubbers alike. Constructed of Baltic Birch, ink, and paper.

Wooden case is 3 in. W x 9 in. L x 2 in. H
